# Sequifi Project Rules

## Writing Rules

When rewriting or generating text:
- Use a professional tone
- Improve grammar
- Improve clarity
- Keep the same meaning
- Avoid unnecessary or repetitive words
- Ensure sentences are concise and easy to read

---

These rules apply automatically when using:
- Rewrite
- Improve Writing
- Rephrase
- Fix Grammar
- Inline AI (Option+L / Alt+L)

